ActPilotage Act
SubjectAtlantic Pilotage Authority's borrowing Limit ** Increase **
PrecisOrder (1) repealing paragraph (b) of Order in Council P.C. 2011-417 of March 10, 2011; and, (2) fixing the maximum amount of money that can be borrowed at any time by the ATLANTIC PILOTAGE AUTHORITY, in Canada or elsewhere for the purpose of defraying its expenses at CAD $15,000,000.
